title: The Coffee Shop
description:
Welcome to episode 24 of Sleep and Relax ASMR! Today's episode features sounds of a busy coffee shop in the UK with plenty of typing, background conversations, coffee making, and more! 

Get in touch with the show: SleepandRelaxASMR@Gmail.com. 

Thanks to Hunski, Eelke, and Digitfishmusic for some of the audio used this episode (freesound.org.).
